{"type": "article", "id": 50867, "title": "这款书架左疏右密，包容你的各种收藏嗜好｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-06T23:22:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 16270, "name": "Industrial Facility"}, {"id": 47514, "name": "Mattiazzi"}, {"id": 44027, "name": "十二时慢"}, {"id": 48226, "name": "ilco"}, {"id": 48227, "name": "Dame"}, {"id": 8331, "name": "吱音"}, {"id": 16057, "name": "Norm Architects"}, {"id": 3255, "name": "Menu"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 162, "image": "img/article/article_show/201803062105481rMApSFfxzOmTQIE.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>LED Carrie Lamp by Norm Architects</h3><p>丹麦工作室 Norm Architects 和丹麦设计品牌 Menu 已经是合作多年的伙伴。他们为 Menu 设计的这款灯具 LED Carrie 透着一股聪明巧妙的劲儿。这是一款便携式 USB 充电灯，可以作为台灯、灯笼、户外灯或是壁灯使用，满足多功能化的个性需求，适用于不同场合。</p><p>圆润的玻璃灯泡配有一个白色或黑色粉末涂层钢制框架，手柄可以自由拆除。售价 199.96 美元，<a href=\"https://store.menudesignshop.com/carrie-portable-led-lamp-p392.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210629HXjMzEYwmrbtl3Ap.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210630m2PRzDf4uSd6pibc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210631usArY5aTo7bq93xv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210631wQzKJqMvHlgPyYN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210632WI7ElgcYbDusw1Um.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210633D9MtJx4aRSfcGOjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803062106353mGgqjM0CfWZOv4V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://minimalissimo.com/led-carrie-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">minimalissimo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>磨彩系列羊绒围巾 by 吱音</h3><p>独立原创设计品牌吱音推出磨彩系列羊绒围巾，以水磨石为设计灵感，仿拟水磨石质朴的肌理，为围巾增加了细腻而独特的质感。明亮灵动的色彩碎片，让围巾简洁又不失趣味。尤其是在春季忽冷忽热的日子中，这都是一件灵活百搭的单品。</p><p>围巾由超纤细纱线织成，羊绒直径仅 15.5 微米，长 34 毫米。触感柔软细腻，轻盈却拥有极高保暖度和亲肤性。售价 599 元，<a href=\"http://b84g6v.ren/cm_details_tkl.php?shopUrl=BzIHMVMwX2YDMwY2UGcBPVI1AGQCOgBu&amp;shop_type=USUDYlVtBGYGZg1k&amp;small_shop_type=BmUEaVBYAGRUMAx%2BUjBcPVJsVHM%3D&amp;buyers_wechat_code=&amp;tbk_y_url=&amp;short_url=rvLq10&amp;unionid=&amp;source=qiange&amp;userid=485631&amp;quser_id=\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210722AVY3c9IdNg1xRFGP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210722GzTAHV0lf2FBo3bw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210722XiVrQLqKmYER7kH4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210723mGcUqniwsNZPzaCh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210725xYHNEsZy5OabhWoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210726KDt7kNjS14OyV8Lo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reusable Tampon Applicator by Dame</h3><p>这种可重复使用的自清洁棉棒敷帖器 D 由初创公司 Dame 设计推出，试图为女性提供一种更可持续的替代方法来替代一次性清洁用品。</p><p>Dame 联合创始人 Celia Pool 和 Alex Mills 的目标是为喜欢使用棉条的女性，提供更可持续的替代产品。用户可以将棉条放入敷帖器的顶部，然后在其末端将棉条推入阴道。但与市面上的产品不同，D 型敷帖器是由抗菌医用级材料制成的，因此它可以重复使用，可使用纸巾擦拭敷帖器并用活水冲洗，隔段时间应该进行适当消毒措施。</p><p>此外，Dame 还推出了一系列有机卫生棉条，不含任何漂白剂、人造丝以及香料。目前，这款产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，套装包括一个敷帖器和 6 个卫生棉条，早鸟价 17 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/517128785/d-the-first-reusable-tampon-applicator/description#\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803062108073dLEciIhlrOnQCta.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210807Zzp2PQt4HSboR5Me.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.360829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210807XnwcQCpoDmqFei63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692470\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210808Z0FaOHM4kDCUij6E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614754\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Into-form: Abstract Seating by ilco</h3><p>Into-form 是一系列模块化组件，单个来看它既不是沙发、椅子，也不是床，但将其排列组合，便能创造出各种需要休闲放松的作为。这个项目最初是由 Koa Pham 和 Madeleine Duflot 提出的，之后Ania Marciniak 加入一起来做，他们三人都是 2016 年中央圣马丁学院的毕业生，毕业后三人组成了设计工作室 ilco，并完善了这一作品。</p><p>五种不同颜色、形状各异的组件可供用户根据需要配置，它既可以是一个艺术装置作品，也可以是提供休闲放松功能的座椅。目前，Into-form 正在 Indiegogo 网站众筹，早鸟价 1500 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/into-form-by-ilco-at-salone-satellite-2018-art-design#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210854hl0iGd6B4egJju5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210854O3GZvAmEN6uJVWfr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210854R7M6rwXlvVE8JNCK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210854t3p9nRgMWcC84EjG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210855iGM8CpdRSqKxA9wu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210855BrXV9EszdWMDKyg4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210855XYqvPIQLynkJHjr9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>万卷书阁 by 十二时慢</h3><p>拥有一个超大空间、隔间合理的书架，是不少书迷的心愿。独立设计品牌十二时慢推出的这款万卷书阁，采用左疏右密的设计，增加了收纳的多样性，陈列摆设一些好看的，收纳存储一些珍藏的。</p><p>玻璃浮门的设计汲取了谷仓滑门的灵感。这款导轨滑门，让柜门隔空而设，不占用空间，又兼具灵动感。每一块竖隔板都可以轻松取出，自然木滑槽，不多占用柜体空间。每一隔间拥有黑胶唱片的高度和深度，足以包容你的各种收藏嗜好。柜体采用传统榫卯结构，结实可靠，牢固耐用。售价 17005 元起，<a href=\"http://www.12h.cn/pc/goods/show?id=73\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210925QzRyNkYFJrW5EHjC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210925LFEzBp6a8m0ZW715.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210928likAEx5FItTGP8m1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306210929hAYWwSQqoGncavJL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306211018WoKqz1cmDxgVvdiU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.143000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Palmo Hook by Industrial Facility for Mattiazzi</h3><p>在今年的斯德哥尔摩设计周期间，意大利设计品牌 Mattiazzi 推出了伦敦设计工作室为其设计的 Palmo 挂钩，可用于在家中悬挂各种物品。</p><p>Palmo 的外形圆润平滑，你可能不会立即把它与常见的挂钩样式联系起来，但它的确很实用，向上弯曲的平滑弧度搭配温润的木材，很适合需要暖意的家居空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803062110515DoxQMfTjFYPa9L7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306211051TcRQdYH1j48fNCZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306211051Dqle23WguNRCGL45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306211051VHuZrRgqyzFvLx89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030621105106fUrHeCThmDLA7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306211051ueZOBFcTEMYWoqPv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/palmo-hook-mattiazzi-sam-hecht-industrial-facility-03-05-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}